data.description: If your looking for a house with potential then look no further! This adorable lil 2 bed 1 bath house would make a great starter home or investment property. It features hardwood floors, a detached garage and main floor laundry. With a little TLC you can easily breath life back into this house to make it a home. Don't judge a book by its cover, come and check it out for yourself!
